    <div class="card">
      <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p><strong>Last update:</strong> 30 August 2025</p>

      <p>This notice explains how <strong>MyHomesBudget</strong> processes personal data for users of the web app at <strong>myhomesbudget.com</strong>.</p>

      <h2>1. Controller</h2>
      <p>MyHomesBudget — Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@myhomesbudget.com">privacy@myhomesbudget.com</a></p>

      <h2>2. Data we process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email</strong> (needed to create the account and authenticate, including Magic Link or Google).</li>
        <li><strong>First name</strong> (optional but recommended to personalize the experience).</li>
        <li>Minimal technical logs and security events.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Purposes & legal bases</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Authentication & account</strong> management (contract).</li>
        <li><strong>Support</strong> and technical communications (legitimate interest/contract).</li>
        <li><strong>Aggregated analytics</strong> and security (legitimate interest, data minimization).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Vendors & transfers</h2>
      <p>We rely on trusted vendors:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong> (EU) for auth/database.</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> for hosting.</li>
        <li><strong>Google</strong> (Identity Services/Analytics) for login and aggregated stats.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>International transfers may occur under Standard Contractual Clauses.</p>

      <h2>5. Retention</h2>
      <p>We keep account data while the service is in use and delete/anonymize within 30 days of account removal unless required otherwise by law.</p>

      <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
      <p>Access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability and objection at
        <a href="mailto:privacy@myhomesbudget.com">privacy@myhomesbudget.com</a>. You may lodge a complaint with your Supervisory Authority.</p>

      <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use strictly necessary cookies and aggregated analytics. Manage preferences via your browser.</p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate measures (encryption in transit/at rest, access controls, backups).</p>

      <h2>9. Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this notice and will inform you of material changes.</p>

